  "texts": [
    "Therefore, some students approach ChatGPT skeptically and do not fully trust it in foreign language learning (Kostka & Toncelli, 2023).",
    "ChatGPT also poses a significant threat to examination processes in learning environments, even causing some universities in Australia to revert to paper-andpencil exams (Cassidy, 2023).",
    "Additionally, there are concerns that chatbots provide data privacy problems (Berşe et al., 2023).",
    "In conclusion, like other chatbots that contribute to foreign language education, ChatGPT has many advantages.",
    "However, the learning environments and tasks assigned to students during its use are critically important (Fryer et al., 2017)."
  ],
